query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  p.addressLine1,
  p.city,
  p.owner1Name,
  p.estimatedValue,
  p.totalBedrooms,
  p.totalBaths,
  COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) as contact_count,
  CASE WHEN pd.id IS NOT NULL THEN 'Yes' ELSE 'No' END as has_deep_search
FROM properties p
LEFT JOIN contacts c ON p.id = c.propertyId
LEFT JOIN propertyDeepSearch pd ON p.id = pd.propertyId
WHERE p.addressLine1 = '4700 SW 18th St' AND p.city = 'West Park'
GROUP BY p.id, p.addressLine1, p.city, p.owner1Name, p.estimatedValue, p.totalBedrooms, p.totalBaths, pd.id;
